-medium-font-size\">感谢您选择WordPress！</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/news/files/2019/11/image.png?fit=632%2C414&amp;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-7755\" /></figure>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:46:\"https://cn.wordpress.org/2019/11/13/kirk/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:73:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:23:\"WordPress 5.2“Jaco”\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:41:\"https://cn.wordpress.org/2019/05/08/jaco/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:49:\"https://cn.wordpress.org/2019/05/08/jaco/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 08 May 2019 00:08:52 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"发布\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://cn.wordpress.org/?p=1199\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:91:\"WordPress 5.2简体中文版现已开放下载，或在您的WordPress仪表盘中升级。\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"Jimmy Xu\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:30967:\"\n<h2 class=\"has-text-align-center\">保护站点安全</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i1.wp.com/wordpress.org/news/files/2019/05/about_maintain-wordpress-cropped.png?fit=632%2C500&amp;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6926\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>WordPress 5.2简体中文版现已<a href=\"https://cn.wordpress.org/download/\">开放下载</a>，或在您的WordPress仪表盘中升级。我们将此版本命名为“Jaco”，以纪念革命性的爵士贝斯手杰可·帕斯透瑞斯。这次更新能够在站点出错时，让您更容易修正您的站点。</p>\n\n\n\n<p>我们为您带来了更健壮的工具，让您识别并修正配置问题及致命错误。不管您是正在帮助客户的开发者，还是正在独立维护您的站点，这些工具都能在您需要时帮您获得正确的信息。</p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\" />\n\n\n\n<h3>站点健康检查</h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"alignleft\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i2.wp.com/wordpress.org/news/files/2019/05/about_site-health.png?resize=205%2C143&amp;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6927\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>基于<a href=\"https://cn.wordpress.org/2019/02/22/betty/\">在5.1中引入的站点健康功能</a>，这次发布加入了两个新页面，帮助您调试常见的配置问题。此发布还加入了让开发者显示调试信息给站点维护者的空间。</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<h3>PHP错误保护</h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"alignleft\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i1.wp.com/wordpress.org/news/files/2019/05/about_error-protection.png?resize=202%2C228&amp;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6930\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>这个针对网站管理员的更新能够让您在不需要开发者协助的情况下，安全地修正及管理致命错误。这个功能特别针对所谓“白屏死机（white screen of death）”的情况，并提供了进入能够暂停造成错误的插件或主题的恢复模式的方式。</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:79px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-default\" />\n\n\n\n<h2>服务所有人的改进</h2>\n\n\n\n<h3>无障碍访问更新</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>此次的数个修改一同为使用屏幕阅读器及其他辅助技术的用户改善了内容感知及键盘导航流程。</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>新的仪表盘图标</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>十三个新图标包含了Instagram、BuddyPress的一篮子图标及旋转的地球图标来包容全球。在仪表盘中寻找他们吧！</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>插件兼容性检查</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>WordPress现在会自动确定您的站点的PHP版本是否与已安装的插件兼容。如果插件需要较您的站点更高版本的PHP，WordPress将不会允许您激活该插件，来帮您防止可能出现的兼容性错误。</p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\" />\n\n\n\n<h2>开发者的小确幸</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns has-2-columns\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n<p><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2019/03/26/coding-standards-updates-for-php-5-6/\"><strong>PHP版本更新</strong></a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>最低支持的PHP版本现在是5.6.20。从WordPress 5.2*开始，主题和插件能够安全地利用命名空间、匿名函数及更多！</p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2019/04/24/developer-focused-privacy-updates-in-5-2/\">隐私更新</a></strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>新的主题页模板、一个条件函数和两个CSS类让设计和自定义隐私政策页面变得更简单。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns has-2-columns\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n<p><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2019/04/24/miscellaneous-developer-updates-in-5-2/\"><strong>新的正文钩子</strong></a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>5.2导入了wp_body_open钩子，让主题能够在&lt;body&gt;元素的开头插入代码。</p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n<p><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2019/03/25/building-javascript/\"><strong>构建JavaScript</strong></a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>通过在wordpress/scripts包中加入webpack和Babel配置，开发者不再需要考虑设置复杂的构建工具就能编写现代JavaScript。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<p><em>* 如果您正在运行古旧版本的PHP（早于5.6.20），请在安装5.2前<a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/update-php/\">更新您的PHP</a>。</em></p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\" />\n\n\n\n<h2>开发团队</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>此次发布由<a href=\"http://ma.tt/\">Matt Mullenweg</a>、<a href=\"https://josepha.blog/\">Josepha Haden Chomphosy</a>和<a href=\"https://pento.net/\">Gary Pendergast</a>领头。他们得到了以下个人的帮助。这次发布包含了561人的贡献，其中更有231人是首次做出贡献。在您喜欢的音乐服务中听听杰可·帕斯透瑞斯，并看看下面这些个人资料吧：<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/aaroncampbell/\">Aaron D. Campbell</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jorbin/\">Aaron Jorbin</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/adamsilverstein/\">Adam Silverstein</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/adamsoucie/\">Adam Soucie</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/oztaser/\">Adil Öztaşer</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ajitbohra/\">Ajit Bohra</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/schlessera/\">Alain Schlesser</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/aldavigdis/\">Alda Vigdís</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/alexdenning/\">Alex Denning</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/xavortm/\">Alex Dimitrov</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/akirk/\">Alex Kirk</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/viper007bond/\">Alex Mills</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tellyworth/\">Alex Shiels</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/lexiqueen/\">Alexis</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/alexislloyd/\">Alexis Lloyd</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/allancole/\">allancole</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/allendav/\">Allen Snook</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/arena/\">Andr?</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/andraganescu/\">andraganescu</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/afercia/\">Andrea Fercia</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/andreamiddleton/\">Andrea Middleton</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/euthelup/\">Andrei Lupu</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/aandrewdixon/\">Andrew Dixon</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/aduth/\">Andrew Duthie</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/nacin/\">Andrew Nacin</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/azaozz/\">Andrew Ozz</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/rarst/\">Andrey &#8220;Rarst&#8221; Savchenko</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/nosolosw/\">Andrés Maneiro</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/afragen/\">Andy Fragen</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/andizer/\">Andy Meerwaldt</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/aniketpatel/\">Aniket Patel</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/anischarolia/\">anischarolia</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/atimmer/\">Anton Timmermans</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/vanyukov/\">Anton Vanyukov</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/avillegasn/\">Antonio Villegas</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/antonypuckey/\">antonypuckey</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/aristath/\">Ari Stathopoulos</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/wpboss/\">Aslam Shekh</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/axaak/\">axaak</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/pixolin/\">Bego Mario Garde</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/empireoflight/\">Ben Dunkle</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/britner/\">Ben Ritner &#8211; Kadence Themes</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bfintal/\">Benjamin Intal</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/billerickson/\">Bill Erickson</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/birgire/\">Birgir Erlendsson</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bodohugobarwich/\">Bodo (Hugo) Barwich</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/gitlost/\">bonger</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/boonebgorges/\">Boone Gorges</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bradleyt/\">Bradley Taylor</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/kraftbj/\">Brandon Kraft</a>、<a href=